OL,7,FThe family of Melvin Cravitz have
OL,8,Fthanked the public for their support
OL,9,Ffollowing his death in the Crumpsall
OL,10,Fterror attack.
OL,12,FMelvin, 66, died in the attack on 2
OL,13,FOctober alongside Adrian Daulby, after
OL,14,Fterrorist Jihad Al-Shamie stabbed him
OL,15,Fmultiple times outside the Heaton Park
OL,16,FHebrew Congregation Synagogue in
OL,17,FCrumpsall, Manchester.
