OL,7,FHis family described him as a "kind
OL,8,Fand caring" husband with a "huge
OL,9,Fcheeky smile" who was "devoted to his
OL,10,Fwife and family."
OL,12,FIn a statement, Melvin's family has
OL,13,Fthanked the public for their support
OL,14,Fduring the weeks since his death.
OL,16,FThey said: "We would like to extend
OL,17,Four deepest and most sincere thanks to
OL,18,Fthe public for all of the messages of
OL,19,Fcondolence, flowers and gifts that
OL,20,Fwere sent as a tribute to Melvin.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
