OL,5,Ccompassion'
OL,7,F"We would also like to thank all of
OL,8,Fthose who attended vigils, lit a
OL,9,Fcandle and carried out a good deed in
OL,10,Fhis memory.
OL,12,F"We want you to know that these
OL,13,Factions and messages of support,
OL,14,Fsolidarity, humanity and compassion
OL,15,Fhave been a great source of strength
OL,16,Fand comfort to us.
