OL,7,FFriends of Melvin's family have also
OL,8,Flaunched a fundraiser to support
OL,9,FMelvin's wife Karen, who he cared for.
OL,11,FThey said: "Melvin was the main
OL,12,Fsupport for his wife... (Who) now
OL,13,Ffaces the unimaginable reality of
OL,14,Fbeing alone while coping with the
OL,15,Ftrauma of what happened. He cared for
OL,16,Fher completely ` doing the shopping,
OL,17,Fcooking, cleaning, and everything that
OL,18,Fmade their home run.
