OL,3,CFamily of Synagogue attack victim
OL,4,Cthank public for 'support and
OL,5,Ccompassion'
OL,7,F"Friends of the family are seeking to
OL,8,Fraise funds to help provide Karen with
OL,9,Fthe care, counselling, and practical
OL,10,Fsupport she now desperately needs. The
OL,11,Fgoal is to give her the stability and
OL,12,Foptions to spend more time with her
OL,13,Ffamily, so that she is not left alone
OL,14,Fin Manchester as she rebuilds her
OL,15,Flife."
OL,17,FThe fundraiser closes on Thursday 6
OL,18,FNovember 2025, and so far has raised
OL,19,Fmore than #25,000.
